{
  "name": "Cobranza Cuotas Pendientes Oficina",
  "nodes": [
    {
      "parameters": {
        "httpMethod": "POST",
        "path": "pending-fees",
        "options": {}
      },
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.webhook",
      "typeVersion": 2.1,
      "position": [-400, 300],
      "id": "webhook-pending-fees",
      "name": "Webhook Cuotas",
      "webhookId": "pending-fees"
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "jsCode": "const items = $input.all();\nconst body = items[0].json.body;\nconst agents = body.agents || [];\nconst sendWhatsApp = body.send_whatsapp !== false;\n\nconst result = [];\nfor (const agent of agents) {\n  if (!agent.email && !agent.phone) continue;\n  result.push({\n    json: {\n      name: agent.name,\n      email: agent.email,\n      phone: (agent.phone || '').replace(/[^0-9]/g, ''),\n      html: agent.html,\n      total: agent.total,\n      whatsapp_message: agent.whatsapp_message || '',\n      send_whatsapp: sendWhatsApp && !!agent.phone\n    }\n  });\n}\n\nreturn result;"
      },
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.code",
      "typeVersion": 2,
      "position": [-160, 300],
      "id": "split-agents",
      "name": "Separar Agentes"
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "sendTo": "={{ $json.email }}",
        "subject": "Cuotas Pendientes de Oficina — Recordatorio de Pago",
        "message": "={{ $json.html }}",
        "options": {
          "appendAttribution": false,
          "senderName": "RE/MAX Exclusive — Administración"
        }
      },
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.gmail",
      "typeVersion": 2.2,
      "position": [80, 300],
      "id": "send-email",
      "name": "Enviar Email Cuota",
      "webhookId": "pending-fees-email"
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "conditions": {
          "options": {
            "caseSensitive": true,
            "leftValue": "",
            "typeValidation": "strict",
            "version": 3
          },
          "conditions": [
            {
              "id": "check-whatsapp",
              "leftValue": "={{ $json.send_whatsapp }}",
              "rightValue": true,
              "operator": {
                "type": "boolean",
                "operation": "equals"
              }
            }
          ],
          "combinator": "and"
        },
        "options": {}
      },
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.if",
      "typeVersion": 2.3,
      "position": [320, 300],
      "id": "check-whatsapp",
      "name": "¿Enviar WhatsApp?"
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "resource": "chat-api",
        "operation": "send-presence",
        "instanceName": "Remax%20Exclusive",
        "remoteJid": "={{ $json.phone }}@s.whatsapp.net",
        "delay": 3000
      },
      "type": "n8n-nodes-evolution-api.evolutionApi",
      "typeVersion": 1,
      "position": [560, 240],
      "id": "typing-wa",
      "name": "Typing WhatsApp",
      "onError": "continueRegularOutput"
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "method": "POST",
        "url": "https://api.remax-exclusive.cl/message/sendText/Remax%20Exclusive",
        "sendHeaders": true,
        "headerParameters": {
          "parameters": [
            {
              "name": "apikey",
              "value": "A47DF197AC02-4F21-BEB4-9F3485E5E4EB"
            },
            {
              "name": "Content-Type",
              "value": "application/json"
            }
          ]
        },
        "sendBody": true,
        "bodyParameters": {
          "parameters": [
            {
              "name": "number",
              "value": "={{ $json.phone }}@s.whatsapp.net"
            },
            {
              "name": "text",
              "value": "={{ $json.whatsapp_message }}"
            }
          ]
        },
        "options": {}
      },
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.httpRequest",
      "typeVersion": 4.2,
      "position": [800, 240],
      "id": "send-wa",
      "name": "Enviar WhatsApp Cuota",
      "retryOnFail": true
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "resource": "chat-api",
        "operation": "read-messages",
        "instanceName": "Remax%20Exclusive",
        "remoteJid": "={{ $json.key.remoteJid }}",
        "messageId": "={{ $json.key.id }}"
      },
      "type": "n8n-nodes-evolution-api.evolutionApi",
      "typeVersion": 1,
      "position": [1040, 240],
      "id": "mark-read-wa",
      "name": "Marcar Leído WA",
      "onError": "continueRegularOutput"
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "content": "## COBRANZA CUOTAS PENDIENTES OFICINA\n\nWebhook recibe del frontend el listado de agentes con deuda.\n\n**Flujo por cada agente:**\n1. Envía email con el HTML pre-armado (tabla de meses pendientes + datos bancarios)\n2. Si tiene teléfono y WhatsApp habilitado → Typing → Enviar mensaje WA → Marcar leído\n\n**Webhook:** POST /webhook/pending-fees\n**Payload:** { send_whatsapp: bool, agents: [{ name, email, phone, html, total, whatsapp_message }] }",
        "height": 320,
        "width": 600
      },
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote",
      "position": [-440, -40],
      "typeVersion": 1,
      "id": "sticky-note-info",
      "name": "Sticky Note"
    }
  ],
  "connections": {
    "Webhook Cuotas": {
      "main": [
        [
          {
            "node": "Separar Agentes",
            "type": "main",
            "index": 0
          }
        ]
      ]
    },
    "Separar Agentes": {
      "main": [
        [
          {
